title: The time has come! Rank Teams!
body:
Hello guys!
I am diamond 4 right now and I am finding it difficult to find people that want to play rank games in a team. SO I decided why not and create one myself. 
The team is called "Boosted Monkeys" with the team tag of "BKEYS". I also have a club named "Boosted Monkey Club" obviously add you to that once you have been added to the rank team. My main roles are all over the place because of been playing since season 2 however I prefer adc>jg>mid. Don't stress about saying the same roles as other people. I am from Melbourne!

So i want a rank team for plats-diamonds (Boosted Monkeys) and another team for any elo (will make team later on, need people!)

If you're interested message me here with your:
